{"tid":300312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"四洲紅燒牛肉大碗麵係我青春","createTime":"2017-06-27T19:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T17:29:34.000Z","uid":106521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffc9298f91bf0bdd9589eb968bda0cc11047a2b","tid":300312,"uid":106521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/032852_920481d4c918ba67f2daf38ce3d5f0fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F032852_920481d4c918ba67f2daf38ce3d5f0fd.jpg&h=16d1fa27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜媽媽真心好想食翻<br />\n<br />\n以前中學考試溫書都有佢陪<br />\n<br />\n個陣惠康百佳都仲有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依加淨番全部滿漢大餐<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知邊到有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a7d5c04e998a5226ca4a33ce82032eb46b92c1","tid":300312,"uid":440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:43:32.000Z","msg":"樓下711"},{"pid":"487c7a9fbc59fd679cdc2b6e0494d1d6b176322a","tid":300312,"uid":106521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓下711</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到樓下？去過好多間都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1d7c787b46eead027eacd1b02d4248b3fe4798","tid":300312,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"食家優惠店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就四洲屋邨擺檔"},{"pid":"c833b4678ba1e07f049524c3c3019c81c7dae49e","tid":300312,"uid":106521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T19:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食家優惠店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就四洲屋邨擺檔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難撞得正有<br />\n<br />\n有冇確實地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"